  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc3\u0dd2  \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dad \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A conditional pardon for Ranjan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickramasinghe today (26) signed the document regarding the granting of conditional presidential pardon to former state minister Ranjan Ramanayake, who was convicted and sentenced to prison for contempt of court.",
        "This pardon comes under the condition that he will not make any statement or act that will insult the court henceforth.",
        "Arrangements have also been made to assign the Secretary of the Ministry of Justice to carry out further work regarding the release of Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake.",
        "Mr. Ranjan Ramanayake issued an affidavit and apologized for insulting the court yesterday (25).",
        "It has been stated in the affidavit that the statements made by him are completely wrong and he apologizes for causing disrespect to everyone in the legal field including the Chief Justice."
      ],
